title: Kids bedtime linked to mums health
text:
Kids bedtime linked to mums' health 
Daily Mail Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
"The late sleepers were considerably more likely to be obese, have a poorer diet, get more screen time and less physical activity than other kids," said lead researcher Professor Tim Olds....
